ru.jango.j0util

Class LogUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.jango.j0util.LogUtil

  • public class LogUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for better log usage: log tag consists of LOG_TAG and class name, so you could filter messages from a certain class.

    LOG_TAG in not final, so u can change it, simply assign:
    LogUtil.LOG_TAG = "some_new_log_tag"
